modified>Sat, 24 Jul 2021 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://www.daoofhealing.org/zh/volunteers/uk-volunteer/</guid><description>01 爱的召唤 - 我在新冠病房当护士的三个月 新冠初期的爆发时，我在英国的一家医院上班。我们都没有足够的经验面临这个疫情的突然降临。病人量的增加让医</description><dc:creator>Dao of Healing</dc:creator><media:content url="https://www.daoofhealing.org/img/uk-volunteer.assets/383px-Flag_of_the_United_Kingdom.svg.png" medium="image"><media:title type="html">featured image</media:title></media:content><category>英国</category><category>新闻动态 &amp; 义工风采 News &amp; Volunteers</category><category>义工风采 Volunteer Stories</category><category>患者反馈 Testimonials</category><category>全球患者反馈 Patient Testimonials</category></item><item><title>多伦多最美的风景</title><link>https://www.daoofhealing.org/zh/volunteers/%E5%A4%9A%E4%BC%A6%E5%A4%9A%E6%9C%80%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF/</link><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Fri, 15 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://www.daoofhealing.org/zh/volunteers/%E5%A4%9A%E4%BC%A6%E5%A4%9A%E6%9C%80%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF/</guid><description>心存芥蒂 珊珊来自深圳，定居加拿大多伦多。三年前家人得重病，为了救助家人，她开始学习中医经方，现在已经是半个医生，统管家人的健康了。三月份，加</description><dc:creator>Dao of Healing</dc:creator><media:content url="https://www.daoofhealing.org//img/%e5%a4%9a%e4%bc%a6%e5%a4%9a%e6%9c%80%e7%be%8e%e7%9a%84%e9%a3%8e%e6%99%af.assets/image-20230303160911561.png" medium="image"><media:title type="html">featured image</media:title></media:content><category>新冠疫情</category><category>多伦多义诊</category><category>新闻动态 &amp; 义工风采 News &amp; Volunteers</category><category>义工风采 Volunteer Stories</category></item><item><title>友善与鼓励:贤小二的'闭关' 义工来稿</title><link>https://www.daoofhealing.org/zh/volunteers/%E5%8F%8B%E5%96%84%E4%B8%8E%E9%BC%93%E5%8A%B1%E8%B4%A4%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8C%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AD%E5%85%B3-%E4%B9%89%E5%B7%A5%E6%9D%A5%E7%A8%BF/</link><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Tue, 05 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://www.daoofhealing.